Congratualtions to our scholars in grades 6-8 who have displayed academic excellence. The Soaring Eagles Award recognizes students who have earned A's & B's, and the Principals Award recognizes students who have earned all A's.
Join us in honoring them.

@Penn Hills Charter PTA

